snippet.title: Multiply & Divide Decimals by 10, 100, and 1000
snippet.description: The shortcut is to simply move the decimal point as many steps as there are zeros in the power of ten. However, I also show what this shortcut for multiplying and dividing decimals is based on, using place value charts.
